\fs30 \cf2 FOR THE FROSTING:
\fs40 \
In a mixing bowl, cream butter, sugar, vanilla and enough cream to achieve desired frosting consistency. Add food coloring if desired. Frost cookies. Sprinkle with colored sugar if desired.\cell \lastrow\row
